This section provides information for contributing to the Asmeta and to use it to develop new tools. The project is now hosted on the github platform, its overview page is https://github.com/asmeta


You can submit [issues](https://github.com/asmeta/asmeta/issues).

Here you can find some information about the <a href="architecture.html">architecture</a> of the Asmeta framework, information about <a href="repository.html">how to access the sources</a>, and a small list of <a href="todos.html">todos</a>.
